Which of the following PAM modules can be used for authorization and authenticationscenarios using external files?
A)  pam_fileauth.so
B)  pam_listfiles.so
C)  pam_filesauth.so
D)  pam_fileauth.so
B
B. The pam_listfiles.so module is used to create scenarios whereby you can createfiles that control authentication and authorization through the PAM system. The other filesare not valid for the scenario described.
